<h2> 1. USER ROUTES </h2>
<hr>
<h3> 1.1. CREATING A NEW USER WITH POST METHOD </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/users/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.2. RETRIEVING ALL USERS WITH GET METHOD </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/users/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.3. RETRIEVING A SPECIFIC USER WITH GET METHOD AND USER ID PASSED AS AN ARGUMENT </h3>
