<h2> 2. MEETUP ROUTES </h2>
<hr>
<h3> 1.1. CREATING A NEW MEETUP WITH POST METHOD </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/meetups/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.2. RETRIEVING ALL MEETUPS WITH GET METHOD </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/meetups/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.3. RETRIEVING A SPECIFIC MEETUP WITH GET METHOD AND USER ID PASSED AS AN ARGUMENT </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/meetups/(id: put meetup id here)
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.4. RESPONDING TO A SPECIFIC MEETUP WITH POST METHOD / MEETUP RSVP </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/meetups/(id: put meetup id here)/rsvps/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.5. RETRIEVING UPCOMING MEETUPS WITH GET METHOD </h3>
<p> 
    https://questioner-web-app.herokuapp.com/api/v1/meetups/upcoming/
</p>
<hr>
<h3> 1.6. DELETING A SPECIFIC MEETUP </h3>
